          "settings": {
            "question": "What is Dreamtape?",
            "answer": "<p>Dreamtape is a mouth tape that gently supports nasal breathing while you sleep. A soft, hypoallergenic strip rests across your closed lips, made from breathable fabric so air can still pass through if needed. Mouth breathing overnight can dry out your airway and disrupt deep sleep, so keeping your lips gently closed helps you settle into quieter, more restful nights.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_use": {
          "type": "qa",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I use Dreamtape?",
            "answer": "<p>Start with clean, dry lips — skip heavy balm or moisturizer beforehand. Peel one strip from the sheet, center it across your closed lips with the breathing slit uncovered, and press the edges down so it feels secure. In the morning, peel it off slowly from one corner for the most comfortable removal.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_safe": {
          "type": "qa",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is mouth taping safe?",
            "answer": "<p>Dreamtape is made for healthy adults with clear nasal breathing. If you have sleep apnea, breathing concerns, blocked nasal passages, or a medical condition, speak with a healthcare professional before use.</p>"
